item.description:
In the previous post we finished working with the orchestration of the containers with docker-compose and we have covered the first three items on the list, and now we are ready to deploy our application on a Kubernetes cluster.
In order to make this possible we are going to follow these steps&hellip;
Create a namespace Create the database deployment, service and the secrets Create the backend deployment, service, secrets and ingress Create the frontend deployment, service, secrets and ingress The Namespace 🔗This is the yaml that we need to create the namespace with:
